        "subject": "LU-9119 lnet: actively push local NI updates to peers",
        "message": "LU-9119 lnet: actively push local NI updates to peers\n\nAdd code to actively push an update of the local NI information to\nthe known peers. This is initiated by lnet_ping_target_update()\nfollowing the installation of a new ln_ping_target (which acts as\nthe source for the pushes). We do not wait for the pushes to\ncomplete.\n\nTest-Parameters: trivial\nSigned-off-by: Olaf Weber <olaf@sgi.com>\nSigned-off-by: Amir Shehata <amir.shehata@intel.com>\nChange-Id: Ic768d0a9e3430067e457eda098864c48988dc842\n"
      },
      "branch": "refs/heads/multi-rail"
    }
